<subSubSection pageId="25" pageNumber="426" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="25.[151,1436,151,285]" pageId="25" pageNumber="426">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,326,188,213]" pageId="25" pageNumber="426">Etymology</emphasis>
. The name is derived from “ 
<emphasis box="[648,726,188,213]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="426">brachy</emphasis>
” (Greek for “short”) and “ 
<emphasis box="[1025,1079,189,212]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="426">gena</emphasis>
” (Greek for “temple”), because of its very short temple.
</paragraph>
